                Scraped real estate + socio-economic data, built predictive models (Regression, RF, XGBoost), and translated findings into actionable insights for investors.
              </p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mt-2">
                <img src="/images/tech/python.svg" alt="Python" class="w-5 h-5" />
                <img src="/images/tech/scikit-learn.svg" alt="scikit-learn" class="w-5 h-5" />
