            <div class="space-y-3 flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">
                <a href="#" class="hover:underline">NYC Taxi Demand Forecasting</a>
              </h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                Time-series modeling of ride demand ‚Üí optimized allocation strategies.
